snippet.title: The Lady Puppet - STEAM Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The announcement trailer for the Steam version of The Lady Puppet!
WISHLIST HERE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1571560/The_Lady_Puppet/

The Lady Puppet is a Survival Horror Adventure game that puts emphasis on atmosphere and exploration. Help Lailah Reah escape from Clawhill, a bizarre world where everyone has been turned into a living puppet. Solve puzzles, use your wits to avoid the enemies and use dolls to summon companions.

A game by: OldPat
Main Sprites by: Sidewinder
Original Soundtrack by: Jasson Prestiliano (JPSoundworks)

JPSoundworks channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/JPSoundworks
